                    <head><hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Bayard</persName> to Mr.
                                <persName type="to">Curry</persName></hi>.</head>
                    <opener><seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg></opener>
                    <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Department
                                    of State</hi>,<lb/><hi rend="italic">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1888-04-21"><hi rend="italic">April</hi> 21,
                            1888</date>.</dateline></opener>
                    <p>Has Cuban budget been presented to the Cortes, and does it contain Mora
                        claim?</p>
                    <closer><signed><hi rend="smallcaps">Bayard.</hi></signed></closer>
                </div>
